.table_shade .odd {
    background: #EEEEEE;
}
.table_shade .even {
    background: #FBFBFB;
}
</style>
<p>
<p>Se <span class="math inline">\(X\)</span> tem densidade <span class="math inline">\(f_X\)</span> e <span class="math inline">\(Y=3X+-1\)</span>, qual é a densidade de <span class="math inline">\(Y\)</span>?</p>
</p>]]></text>
</questiontext>
<generalfeedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<p>A inversa é <span class="math inline">\(x=(y--1)/3\)</span> e seu jacobiano absoluto é <span class="math inline">\(1/3\)</span>. Portanto,
<span class="math display">\[f_Y(y)=\frac1{3}f_X\left(\frac{y--1}{3}\right).\]</span></p>
</p>]]></text>
</generalfeedback>
<penalty>0</penalty>
<defaultgrade>1</defaultgrade>
<shuffleanswers>false</shuffleanswers>
<single>true</single>
<answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
<answer fraction="100" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(f_Y(y)=\dfrac1{3}f_X\!\left(\dfrac{y--1}{3}\right)\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(f_Y(y)=\dfrac1{9}f_X(y/3--1)\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(f_Y(y)=f_X(y--1)\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(f_Y(y)=3f_X(3y+-1)\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(f_Y(y)=f_X((y+-1)/3)\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
</question>


