    background: #FBFBFB;
}
</style>
<p>
<p>Se <span class="math inline">\(U\sim U(0,1)\)</span> e <span class="math inline">\(Y=-\log(1-U)/1\)</span>, qual é a distribuição de <span class="math inline">\(Y\)</span>?</p>
</p>]]></text>
</questiontext>
<generalfeedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<p>Para <span class="math inline">\(y&gt;0\)</span>,
<span class="math display">\[P(Y\leq y)=P\{U\leq1-e^{-1y}\}
=1-e^{-1y},\]</span>
que é a FDA exponencial de taxa 1.</p>
</p>]]></text>
</generalfeedback>
<penalty>0</penalty>
<defaultgrade>1</defaultgrade>
<shuffleanswers>false</shuffleanswers>
<single>true</single>
<answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Gama com forma 1 e taxa 1.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Exponencial com taxa <span class="math inline">\(1/1\)</span>, pois <span class="math inline">\(F_Y(y)=e^{-y/1}\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Normal com média <span class="math inline">\(1/1\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Uniforme em <span class="math inline">\((0,1/1)\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="100" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Exponencial com taxa 1, pois <span class="math inline">\(F_Y(y)=1-e^{-1y}\)</span> para <span class="math inline">\(y&gt;0\)</span>.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
</question>


